    <refsection>
      <title>Description</title>

      <para>The <command>ss-upload</command> command will upload the given
      <replaceable>file</replaceable> into the
      <replaceable>destination</replaceable>, a location in S3. The format of
      <replaceable>destination</replaceable> is
      <replaceable>bucket-name</replaceable>:[<replaceable>path</replaceable>].
      The <replaceable>username</replaceable> and
      <replaceable>password</replaceable> are only required when running the
      command standalone outside of a SlipStream execution.</para>
    </refsection>

